battle_nickz_minecraft is simply a small map to battle on, Which contains a bunch of boosters for you to gain plenty of speed on. This map would be fun for people who like to bhop/surf because there is a lot of strafing and bhopping. There is no need to change your servers settings because it automatically changes it for you (airaccelerate, enablebunnyhopping, buytime, starting money and enableboost)

This map is pretty much based on my older map (battle_nickz) but changed the spawns, cleaned it up abit and re textured with Minecraft Textures.

It is a small fun map to battle on, It's more of like a bhopping battle map. The arena has boosters which you can bhop off to get a lot of speed. My map also automatically sets the cvars (Like sv_airaccelerate and sv_enablebunnyhopping) For you to just load up the map and play. I hope you enjoy it :)

This is my second attempt at this map here is a link to the first Combine Battle Ground. I will be releasing a final version within a month or so, I would appreciate feed back so I know what to start on for the final version.
Description: For the Most part the layout is the same as the first map Combine Battle Ground but there are some changes. In general the map is lighter, there is fog, and the map is more wide. On the top floor there There is a large median that seperates the left and right. you can get on top of the median and go to the left and right sides where it wings out. there is also 2 small rooms on each side(left and right) that can be used as cover aswell as the many crates. On the bottom floor it is much darker and more open. Most of the cover is near the enterances to the bottom floor. In the middle there is no cover, because it's the darkest part of the map. This allows some stealth.
As far as credits go I'm the only one who work on this map and I used source sdk. *Note: Do not copy, modify, or redistribute this map, without author consent*

ar_well is a port of the cp_well map from the Team Fortress 2 (tf2) game.

Facts

Well is one of four maps that are remakes of maps from Team Fortress Classic. At the same time, the map is very different from its predecessor - the emphasis is on the depot rather than on any well (Well in English sounds like "well").

ar_shoots is a port of the ar_shoots map from the Counter-Strike: Global Offensive game.

The map takes place somewhere in Vietnam.

Ar_shoots is a symmetrical map. The terrorist and spetsnaz revival bases are located opposite each other with the same cover for both sides.

The official factions of the map are Pirates (terrorist team) and GIGN (special forces team).

ar_pond is a port with remake of the aim_pond map from the Counter-Strike: Global Offensive game.

- This is not a large map, which will most likely be more interesting to play with sniper rifles.

ar_park is a port with remake of the ar_park from the Counter-Strike: Global Offensive game.

The game takes place in a park located in a rural urban-type settlement. The map is not big at all.

As promised earlier:

ar_hide_and_seek_house_lite is a port of stripped-down vershion the hide_and_seek_house20 map from the CSGO game.

Description of the map from the author:

This is a map for hide and seek. There are lots of cool hideouts and passages on the map. I tried to make every element on the map perfectly finished the way I wanted. There is one interesting place worth seeing Have fun.

Map AIM_MAZE
Version 1.0 - Beta

Hey There, This is my 2nd Map for CS:S.
This Map is about a Big Maze Where CTs and Ts Fight Each Other.
Don't Worry, It's Not Very Complex and Big So you Don't get Lost easily.

(That Would be Great if I See This Map in a Server :D)

Installation:
Simply Extract the cstrike Folder to your Counter-Strike: Source Directory. (e.g. D:\Games\CSS)

Features:
Working Cubemaps for Both LDR and HDR.
Optimized Map using Nodraws, Areaportals and Occluders.
Bot Pathfinding is Good.

aim_downtownbattle
Created by Le M

This map was created in three days of work.
Into it, you can take place in a battle into a destructed city center.
The terrorists spawn in a warehouse, while the counter terrorists spawn behind the buildings. That's a battle arena. The only goal to reach is to kill the opposite team.
There're two hidden weapons in the map.

Have a good game !
